follow all the commands here_
https://docs.ros.org/en/humble/Installation/Ubuntu-Install-Debs.html

after finish, everytime you run ros2humble you should do first(in every terminal that you want to use the ros):

source /opt/ros/humble/setup.bash

to avoid using this do once to add it into oto execution during terminal openning:

sudo apt install gedit

 gedit ~/.bashrc


add to the end of the file "source /opt/ros/humble/setup.bash" with out quotes-



now you can run talker listener examples.


rqt_graph is ros tool that shows active tool relations graphically



sudo apt install python3-colcon-common-extensions


cd /usr/share/colcon_argcomplete/hook

 gedit ~/.bashrc

att the end of document put this line:
source /usr/share/colcon_argcomplete/hook/colcon-argcomplete.bash

then save the file and exit.
then do on every open terminal :

source  ~/.bashrc










